\begin_layout Subsubsection*

\lang english
6.4 Service Improvement Plan
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
A Service Improvement Plan (SIP) is required for any SIR entry routed through the project path.
 The SIP serves as the project initiation document submitted to the IT Director for charter approval under 
\series bold
Policy 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
