reference "pol:5.10"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"
nolink "false"

\end_inset


\series default
 annual maturity review cycle.
 The summary is the evidentiary record that the improvement intake function is operating.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
Annual improvement summaries shall be retained permanently in accordance with NRS 239.125 and the Nevada Local Government Records Retention Schedule:
 LRDA 20071558 (Activity Reports).
\end_layout

